{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Now, if President Obama"},{"time":3000,"text":"invited me to be the next Czar of Mathematics,"},{"time":7000,"text":"then I would have a suggestion for him"},{"time":10000,"text":"that I think would vastly improve"},{"time":12000,"text":"the mathematics education in this country."},{"time":15000,"text":"And it would be easy to implement"},{"time":17000,"text":"and inexpensive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"The mathematics curriculum that we have"},{"time":21000,"text":"is based on a foundation of arithmetic and algebra."},{"time":25000,"text":"And everything we learn after that"},{"time":27000,"text":"is building up towards one subject."},{"time":30000,"text":"And at top of that pyramid, it's calculus."},{"time":34000,"text":"And I'm here to say"},{"time":36000,"text":"that I think that that is the wrong summit of the pyramid ..."},{"time":40000,"text":"that the correct summit -- that all of our students,"},{"time":42000,"text":"every high school graduate should know --"},{"time":44000,"text":"should be statistics:"},{"time":47000,"text":"probability and statistics."},{"time":49000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"I mean, don't get me wrong. Calculus is an important subject."},{"time":55000,"text":"It's one of the great products of the human mind."},{"time":57000,"text":"The laws of nature are written in the language of calculus."},{"time":61000,"text":"And every student who studies math, science, engineering, economics,"},{"time":65000,"text":"they should definitely learn calculus"},{"time":67000,"text":"by the end of their freshman year of college."},{"time":69000,"text":"But I'm here to say, as a professor of mathematics,"},{"time":72000,"text":"that very few people actually use calculus"},{"time":76000,"text":"in a conscious, meaningful way, in their day-to-day lives."},{"time":79000,"text":"On the other hand,"},{"time":81000,"text":"statistics -- that's a subject that you could,"},{"time":84000,"text":"and should, use on daily basis. Right?"},{"time":87000,"text":"It's risk. It's reward. It's randomness."},{"time":90000,"text":"It's understanding data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"I think if our students, if our high school students --"},{"time":94000,"text":"if all of the American citizens --"},{"time":96000,"text":"knew about probability and statistics,"},{"time":99000,"text":"we wouldn't be in the economic mess that we're in today. (Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":102000,"text":"Not only -- thank you -- not only that ..."},{"time":105000,"text":"but if it's taught properly, it can be a lot of fun."},{"time":108000,"text":"I mean, probability and statistics,"},{"time":110000,"text":"it's the mathematics of games and gambling."},{"time":114000,"text":"It's analyzing trends. It's predicting the future."},{"time":118000,"text":"Look, the world has changed"},{"time":120000,"text":"from analog to digital."},{"time":123000,"text":"And it's time for our mathematics curriculum to change"},{"time":126000,"text":"from analog to digital,"},{"time":128000,"text":"from the more classical, continuous mathematics,"},{"time":132000,"text":"to the more modern, discrete mathematics --"},{"time":135000,"text":"the mathematics of uncertainty,"},{"time":137000,"text":"of randomness, of data --"},{"time":139000,"text":"that being probability and statistics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"In summary, instead of our students"},{"time":144000,"text":"learning about the techniques of calculus,"},{"time":147000,"text":"I think it would be far more significant"},{"time":150000,"text":"if all of them knew what two standard deviations"},{"time":153000,"text":"from the mean means. And I mean it."},{"time":156000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":158000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}